### <a id="cron"></a> Valid cron Input Verification

For `string` type form fields in tiles, Ops Manager supports a `constraints.must_be_cron_schedule` attribute
that verifies whether the input is a valid `cron` expression.
Tiles can use this attribute for fields that schedule backups, for example.
For information about the `string` blueprint type,
see [string](http://docs.pivotal.io/tiledev/property-template-references.html#string).


